description: Main entry point of a Flutter application that sets up theming, navigation, and initial screens for a preference matching app.

classes.name: MyApp
classes.description: Root widget setting up theme and top-level provider for the app.

classes.name: MyHomePage
classes.description: Main screen widget with bottom navigation and filter access.

methods.name: _buildTheme
methods.description: Constructs and returns the ThemeData used by the app, defining colors, text styles, and component themes.

methods.name: build
methods.description: Builds the widget tree for MyApp and MyHomePage, setting up providers and UI.

methods.name: _openFilters
methods.description: Navigates to the FilterScreen when the filters button is pressed.

methods.name: _buildHomePlaceholder
methods.description: Returns a placeholder widget indicating that app content is being generated.
